properties.name: Medivet
properties.wheelchair:description: Fairly narrow front door, small step. Ok for some wheelchair with kerb climber ... but bumpy ride. Waiting room accessible, consulting room accessible but small. Staff friendly and helpful.

properties.description: Large area surrounded with fence and gates, open to anyone, used by locals for dog walking.
